text.tspan: Monthly confirmed cases of influenza A
This includes confirmed cases of all strains of influenza A virus. Only a fraction of potential cases of influenza
are tested by labs to confirm whether they have influenza and to identify their strain. The level of testing may
vary between countries and over time.
Data source: FluNet by the World Health Organization (2023)
